definitions.definition: The skin of a sheep , especially an adult sheep, and especially when used to make parchment or in bookbinding .

subdefinitions.definition: The tanned skin of a sheep with the fleece left on, especially when used for clothing , rugs , etc.

definitions.definition: A diploma , especially the one representing a university or college degree .

main_definition: ( uncountable ) The skin of a sheep , especially an adult sheep, and especially when used to make parchment or in bookbinding .
secondary_definitions: ( US , countable ) A diploma , especially the one representing a university or college degree .
